citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:30 am on
02/18/2015.
APHIS VMO contacted the licensee via telephone and it was determined that no one was available to go on
inspection.
Additional Inspectors
Rhodes Cindy, Animal Care Inspector
